attributes.Long form description: The instructor tells him to disassemble this small shelf from IKEA. The student unscrews the first leg, then the second leg. After he disassemble the second leg, he then disassembles the third leg, then disassembles the fourth leg. Then he disassembles the shelf. Finally he disassembles the top table with the second leg.

attributes.Transcription: Well now disassemble this small shelf from Ikea, so please go ahead.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the first leg.
The student unscrews the second leg.
The student disassembles the first leg.
The student disassembles the third leg.
The student disassembles the fourth leg.
The student returns and unscrews the hex socket head from the second leg.
